Job Description
Now recruiting:
Cleveland Clinic Abu Dhabi, brought to you by Mubadala Healthcare, is a world-class multispecialty hospital being built in Abu Dhabi that will bring more than 30 medical and surgical specialties across 12 Institutes.
We are looking for talented UAE National and Expatriate team players who have a passion to put 'patients first' and who are looking to grow and develop their career in a dynamic healthcare organization.
